org.nd4j.autodiff.listeners

Class ListenerVariables

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nd4j.autodiff.listeners.ListenerVariables

  • public class ListenerVariables
extends Object
    Specifies a Listener's required variables for each operation. Used to ensure those variables end up in the minimum required subgraph calculated by InferenceSession. Otherwise, if the variables weren't required by a loss variable, they would not be calculated.

    Any variables in here are guaranteed to have Listener.activationAvailable(SameDiff, At, MultiDataSet, SameDiffOp, String, INDArray) called for them.
